<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NSL Click & Work - Student Journey</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --nsl-red: #cc1f1f;
            --nsl-gold: #f2a900;
            --nsl-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --nsl-light: #f5f5f5;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #e0e0e0;
            color: var(--nsl-dark);
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact !important;
            print-color-adjust: exact !important;
        }
        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm;
            background: white;
            margin: 20px auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            page-break-after: always;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        @media print {
            body { background: white; margin: 0; }
            .page { margin: 0; box-shadow: none; width: 210mm; height: 297mm; page-break-after: always; }
            @page { size: A4 portrait; margin: 0; }
            .top-controls { display: none !important; }
        }

        /* ===== TOP CONTROLS ===== */
        .top-controls {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        .lang-switch { display: flex; gap: 5px; }
        .lang-btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .lang-btn.active { background: var(--nsl-dark); color: white; }
        .print-btn {
            background: var(--nsl-red); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 5px 15px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .print-btn:hover { background: #a11818; }

        /* ===== PAGE 1 LAYOUT ===== */
        .hero-band {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
            padding: 36px 44px 28px;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-band::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -60px; right: -60px;
            width: 280px; height: 280px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(242,169,0,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .hero-band::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -40px; left: 30%;
            width: 200px; height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(204,31,31,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .logo-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero-tag {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            color: var(--nsl-gold);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .hero-h1 {
            font-size: 44px;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.05;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0 0 14px 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero-sub {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #bbb;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 85%;
            margin: 0 0 24px 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero-stat {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--nsl-gold);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .hero-stat .num { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--nsl-gold); line-height: 1; }
        .hero-stat .lbl { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #aaa; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 4px; }

        /* ===== DIAGONAL DIVIDER ===== */
        .diagonal {
            width: 100%;
            height: 40px;
            background: white;
            clip-path: polygon(0 100%, 100% 0, 100% 100%);
            margin-top: -1px;
        }

        /* ===== RED ACCENT BAR ===== */
        .accent-bar {
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--nsl-red) 0%, var(--nsl-gold) 100%);
        }

        /* ===== TIMELINE SECTION ===== */
        .timeline-section {
            padding: 24px 44px;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .section-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            color: var(--nsl-red);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--nsl-dark);
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        }

        .timeline-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px 20px;
        }
        .step-card {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: var(--nsl-light);
            border-left: 4px solid #ddd;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .step-card.active { border-left-color: var(--nsl-red); background: #fff5f5; }
        .step-card.done { border-left-color: var(--nsl-gold); background: #fffbf0; }
        .step-badge {
            width: 36px; height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #ddd;
            color: #666;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .step-card.active .step-badge { background: var(--nsl-red); color: white; }
        .step-card.done .step-badge { background: var(--nsl-gold); color: var(--nsl-dark); }
        .step-card h4 { margin: 0 0 3px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--nsl-dark); }
        .step-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666; line-height: 1.4; }

        /* ===== MOCKUP VISUAL ===== */
        .mockup-strip {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--nsl-red) 0%, #a11818 100%);
            margin-top: auto;
            padding: 20px 44px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .mockup-strip::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -60px; right: -20px;
            width: 200px; height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .mockup-img {
            width: 180px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            box-shadow: 10px 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            transform: perspective(800px) rotateY(8deg) rotateX(-3deg);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .mockup-text { color: white; flex: 1; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        .mockup-text h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 8px 0; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .mockup-text p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin: 0 0 14px 0; line-height: 1.5; }
        .badge-pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            color: white;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        /* ===== FOOTER BAND (PAGE 1) ===== */
        .footer-band {
            background: var(--nsl-light);
            padding: 16px 44px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--nsl-gold);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .footer-band p { margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #555; }
        .footer-band a { color: var(--nsl-red); font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; }
        .page-num { font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; font-weight: 600; }

        /* ===== PAGE 2 ===== */
        .p2-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--nsl-red) 0%, #a11818 100%);
            padding: 30px 44px;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .p2-hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50px; right: -30px;
            width: 220px; height: 220px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .p2-hero-tag { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2.5px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .p2-hero h2 { font-size: 38px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 12px 0; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        .p2-hero p { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 90%; margin: 0; position: relative; z-index: 1; }

        /* USP CARDS */
        .usp-section {
            padding: 24px 44px;
        }
        .usp-cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        .usp-card {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .usp-card.dark { background: var(--nsl-dark); color: white; }
        .usp-card.gold { background: var(--nsl-gold); color: var(--nsl-dark); }
        .usp-card.light { background: var(--nsl-light); color: var(--nsl-dark); border: 2px solid #e8e8e8; }
        .usp-card.red-outline { background: white; color: var(--nsl-dark); border: 2px solid var(--nsl-red); }
        .usp-card .icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
        .usp-card h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 6px 0; }
        .usp-card p { font-size: 13px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; opacity: 0.85; }

        /* SCORE VISUAL */
        .score-section {
            margin: 0 44px;
            background: var(--nsl-dark);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
            color: white;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* BOOKING BAND */
        .booking-band {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0 44px;
            background: white;
        }
        .booking-inner {
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px dashed #ddd;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 28px 40px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .booking-inner .book-tag {
            font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            color: var(--nsl-red); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .booking-inner h3 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: var(--nsl-dark); }
        .booking-inner p { font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin: 0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.5; }
        .book-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: var(--nsl-dark);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 3px solid var(--nsl-red);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .score-circle {
            width: 90px; height: 90px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: conic-gradient(var(--nsl-gold) 0deg, var(--nsl-gold) 245deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 245deg);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .score-circle::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--nsl-dark);
        }
        .score-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; }
        .score-inner .score-num { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--nsl-gold); line-height: 1; }
        .score-inner .score-lbl { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .score-text h4 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 6px 0; color: white; }
        .score-text p { font-size: 13px; color: #aaa; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }

        /* CTA FOOTER (PAGE 2) */
        .cta-footer {
            background: var(--nsl-dark);
            padding: 22px 44px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .cta-left h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; color: white; margin: 0 0 4px 0; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .cta-left p { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin: 0; }
        .cta-btn {
            background: var(--nsl-gold);
            color: var(--nsl-dark);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 0;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: 3px solid var(--nsl-gold);
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0px rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            transform: rotate(-1deg);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="top-controls">
        <div class="lang-switch">
            <a href="?lang=en" class="lang-btn <%= lang === 'en' ? 'active' : '' %>">EN</a>
            <a href="?lang=de" class="lang-btn <%= lang === 'de' ? 'active' : '' %>">DE</a>
        </div>
        <button onclick="window.print()" class="print-btn">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 6 2 18 2 18 9"></polyline><path d="M6 18H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><rect x="6" y="14" width="12" height="8"></rect></svg>
            PDF / Print
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- PAGE 1: HERO + JOURNEY TIMELINE                              -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <div class="page">
        <!-- HERO BAND -->
        <div class="hero-band">
            <div class="logo-row">
                <img src="/assets/design/NSL_logo_mid.png" alt="NSL" style="height: 48px;">
                <img src="/assets/design/Logo_Mid_PersonalKampagne.png" alt="PersonalKampagne" style="height: 30px;">
            </div>
            <div class="hero-tag">Your Career. Your Future.</div>
            <h1 class="hero-h1">Your Journey<br>to Germany.</h1>
            <p class="hero-sub">The NSL Click & Work Portal gives you complete visibility and control over your entire career migration process — from assessment to arrival.</p>
            <div class="hero-stats">
                <div class="hero-stat">
                    <div class="num">21</div>
                    <div class="lbl">EU Countries</div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stat">
                    <div class="num">400k+</div>
                    <div class="lbl">Talent Network</div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stat">
                    <div class="num">100%</div>
                    <div class="lbl">GDPR Secure</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accent-bar"></div>

        <!-- TIMELINE SECTION -->
        <div class="timeline-section">
            <div class="section-label">Step-by-Step Process</div>
            <div class="section-title">6 Steps to Your Dream Job</div>

            <div class="timeline-grid">
                <div class="step-card active">
                    <div class="step-badge">1</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Assessment Test</h4>
                        <p>Complete our comprehensive IQ, decision-making & skills assessment. Get your NSL-Score.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card done">
                    <div class="step-badge">2</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Interview & Media</h4>
                        <p>Record your introduction video and profile photo. We build your professional Setcard.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-badge">3</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Profile Live</h4>
                        <p>Your profile goes live. Verified German employers can now discover and view your Setcard.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-badge">4</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Employer Match</h4>
                        <p>A German employer selects your profile. You enter direct consideration for a position.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-badge">5</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Contract & Integration</h4>
                        <p>Sign your employment contract. Begin language and cultural integration courses.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-badge">6</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Visa & Departure</h4>
                        <p>Complete visa processing, book your flight. Welcome to Germany! 🇩🇪</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SETCARD MOCKUP STRIP -->
        <div class="mockup-strip">
            <img src="/images/marketing/setcard_modal.png" class="mockup-img" alt="Your Setcard">
            <div class="mockup-text">
                <h3>Your Professional Setcard</h3>
                <p>We create a stunning, standardized digital resume (Setcard) from your photo, video, NSL-Score, and professional data — instantly visible to 1,000+ German employers on the portal.</p>
                <span class="badge-pill">⭐ Auto-generated by NSL</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <div class="footer-band">
            <p>Student Portal: <a href="https://www.personalkampagne-portal.de">www.personalkampagne-portal.de</a></p>
            <span class="page-num">1 / 2</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- PAGE 2: USP + NSL-SCORE + CTA                               -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <div class="page">
        <!-- RED HERO BAND -->
        <div class="p2-hero">
            <div class="p2-hero-tag">Why NSL Click & Work</div>
            <h2>Why Choose<br>the NSL Portal?</h2>
            <p>We don't just connect you with a job — we manage your entire relocation journey, from documents and visa to cultural integration and long-term support.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- USP CARDS -->
        <div class="usp-section">
            <div class="section-label">Your Advantages</div>
            <div class="usp-cards">
                <div class="usp-card dark">
                    <span class="icon">📱</span>
                    <h4>Real-Time Tracking</h4>
                    <p>Log in anytime with your student ID to see your current step, status, and NSL-Score live on the portal.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="usp-card gold">
                    <span class="icon">🤖</span>
                    <h4>AI-Powered Matching</h4>
                    <p>Our Sharkie AI analyses your profile and skills to match you with the most relevant German employers automatically.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="usp-card red-outline">
                    <span class="icon">🛡️</span>
                    <h4>Full Visa & Relocation</h4>
                    <p>NSL handles document translation, professional recognition, visa processing, and cultural integration from A to Z.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="usp-card light">
                    <span class="icon">🎥</span>
                    <h4>Video Introduction</h4>
                    <p>A 60-second intro video lets German employers know you personally before any interview, boosting your selection chances.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- NSL-SCORE VISUAL -->
        <div class="score-section">
            <div class="score-circle">
                <div class="score-inner">
                    <div class="score-num">48+</div>
                    <div class="score-lbl">Benchmark</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="score-text">
                <h4>The NSL-Score: Your Competitive Edge</h4>
                <p>Every candidate receives a verified NSL-Score based on comprehensive IQ, decision-making, and soft skills assessments. A score of 48+ places you in the top percentile — the benchmark German employers trust and prefer.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BOOKING BAND -->
        <div class="booking-band">
            <div class="booking-inner">
                <div class="book-tag">Next Step</div>
                <h3>📅 Schedule Your Interview</h3>
                <p>Ready to take the first step? Book an onboarding appointment with your local NSL center and start your journey to Germany today.</p>
                <a href="https://www.personalkampagne-portal.de" class="book-btn">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
                    Book Onboarding Appointment
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA FOOTER -->
        <div class="cta-footer">
            <div class="cta-left">
                <h3>Ready to start your journey?</h3>
                <p>Ask your local NSL center for details or login at the Student Portal.</p>
                <p style="color: #f2a900; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 4px;">🌐 www.personalkampagne-portal.de</p>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                <img src="/assets/design/NSL_logo_mid.png" alt="NSL" style="height: 40px; opacity: 0.8;">
                <span class="page-num" style="color: #555;">2 / 2</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
